<section class="container mt-5">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: May 1, 2025</p>

    <p>Your privacy matters. This online diary is a personal space for your thoughts and memories. Here's how we handle your data:</p>

    <h4>1. What We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Entries you create and edit in your diary</li>
        <li>Your login and registration data (if applicable)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2. How We Use It</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To save and display your diary entries securely</li>
        <li>To provide personalized access to your content</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. We Don't Share</h4>
    <p>We will never share your personal data with third parties.</p>

    <h4>4. Your Control</h4>
    <p>You can edit or delete your diary entries anytime. Your data is yours.</p>

    <h4>5. Security</h4>
    <p>We use encryption and secure storage methods to protect your content.</p>

    <h4>6. Changes</h4>
    <p>If we change this policy, we’ll notify you on the homepage or through your account.</p>

    <p class="mt-4">Questions? Contact us via the support page.</p>
</section>

